### Core Role Access (Already Configured)

| Role | Database Access | Warehouse Access |
|------|-----------------|------------------|
| `{{ prefix }}_READ` | DB_R (all zones) | All warehouses |
| `{{ prefix }}_WRITE` | DB_W (all zones) | All warehouses |
| `{{ prefix }}_CREATE` | DB_C (all zones) | All warehouses |
| `{{ prefix }}_ADMIN` | Full ownership | All warehouses |

### Custom Role Access Status

{%- if custom_read_roles %}

| Role | Data Access | Warehouse Access |
|------|-------------|------------------|
{%- for role in custom_read_roles %}
| `{{ prefix }}_CUSTOM_{{ role.name | upper }}` | {{ role.schema_access }} | **Needs Grant** |
{%- endfor %}

Custom roles require explicit warehouse grants to execute queries.

{%- else %}

No custom read roles configured. All access is through core roles.

{%- endif %}

### Available Warehouse Access Roles

{%- for wh in warehouse_configuration %}
| `{{ prefix }}_WH_U_{{ wh.name | upper }}` | USAGE on `{{ prefix }}_WH_{{ wh.name | upper }}` |
{%- endfor %}

### Grant Warehouse Access to Custom Roles

To grant warehouse access to a custom role:

```sql
USE ROLE {{ prefix }}_RBAC;
GRANT ROLE {{ prefix }}_WH_U_<warehouse> TO ROLE {{ prefix }}_CUSTOM_<name>;
```
